<br>
If he were not to do this, especially in a PoP zone where an unslowed mob will rip any tank a new arse in a matter of seconds, you could end up at worse with a dead tank or at best a healer lower on mana than he need be.  <br>
<br>
Hence the reason why frequent calls of &quot;Any slower looking for a group?&quot; can be heard echoing around the Planes..... heh.  <br>
<br>
Just my 2cp.... <br>
