<br>
Warrior taunt should be more or less equal to hybrid taunt.<br>
<br>
That way, if you're looking for a tank you really aren't sure which class to choose, since marginally better hps is balanced by the spells that hybrids can cause.<br>
<br>
This is how it should be.<br>
<br>
Giving warriors more dps will not increase their lfg chances. All it will do is let them get rejected twice over.<br>
<br>
(Hey, we need a tank, what about the warr... oh wait here's a paladin. Hey, we need dps, what about the warr... oh wait, here's a ranger).<br>
